            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-7174.xml" resp="#automat">letter from L. C. Wedgwood, [25 April 1870]</ref> and n. 2.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">In <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_2400.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Expression</hi></ref>, pp. 147–54, CD discussed facial expressions associated with crying in infants, but did not mention Wedgwood. The baby Wedgwood observed may have been her nephew, Hervey Wedgwood Williams.</note>
